[
    {
        "text": "The History of English in Ten Minutes.",
        "startTime": 4702,
        "endTime": 6697,
        "slowStartTime": 7203,
        "slowEndTime": 10271
    },
    {
        "text": "Chapter ten, global English or whose language is it anyway?",
        "startTime": 7031,
        "endTime": 10643,
        "slowStartTime": 10696,
        "slowEndTime": 16189
    },
    {
        "text": "In the 15 hundred years since the Romans left Britain,...",
        "startTime": 11505,
        "endTime": 13873,
        "slowStartTime": 17408,
        "slowEndTime": 21035
    },
    {
        "text": "...English has shown a unique ability to absorb, evolve, invade...",
        "startTime": 14177,
        "endTime": 17119,
        "slowStartTime": 21415,
        "slowEndTime": 25904
    },
    {
        "text": "...and if we're honest, steal.",
        "startTime": 17380,
        "endTime": 18356,
        "slowStartTime": 26220,
        "slowEndTime": 27759
    },
    {
        "text": "After foreign settlers got it started,...",
        "startTime": 18719,
        "endTime": 20283,
        "slowStartTime": 28229,
        "slowEndTime": 30650
    },
    {
        "text": "...it grew into a fully-fledged language all of its own...",
        "startTime": 20568,
        "endTime": 22880,
        "slowStartTime": 31002,
        "slowEndTime": 34545
    },
    {
        "text": "...before leaving home and traveling the world.",
        "startTime": 23193,
        "endTime": 24922,
        "slowStartTime": 34939,
        "slowEndTime": 37608
    },
    {
        "text": "First via the high seas, then via the high-speed broadband connection,...",
        "startTime": 25197,
        "endTime": 28679,
        "slowStartTime": 37946,
        "slowEndTime": 43244
    },
    {
        "text": "...pilfering words from over 350 languages...",
        "startTime": 29000,
        "endTime": 31418,
        "slowStartTime": 43650,
        "slowEndTime": 47352
    },
    {
        "text": "...and establishing itself as a global institution.",
        "startTime": 31619,
        "endTime": 33876,
        "slowStartTime": 47578,
        "slowEndTime": 51039
    },
    {
        "text": "All this despite a written alphabet that bears no correlation to how it sounds...",
        "startTime": 34346,
        "endTime": 38145,
        "slowStartTime": 51669,
        "slowEndTime": 57442
    },
    {
        "text": "...and a system of spelling that even Dan Brown couldn't decipher.",
        "startTime": 38413,
        "endTime": 41193,
        "slowStartTime": 57769,
        "slowEndTime": 62014
    },
    {
        "text": "Right now, around 1.5 billion people speak English.",
        "startTime": 41817,
        "endTime": 44892,
        "slowStartTime": 62875,
        "slowEndTime": 67563
    },
    {
        "text": "Of these, about a quarter are native speakers,...",
        "startTime": 45347,
        "endTime": 47369,
        "slowStartTime": 68170,
        "slowEndTime": 71278
    },
    {
        "text": "...a quarter speak it as their second language...",
        "startTime": 47684,
        "endTime": 49441,
        "slowStartTime": 71676,
        "slowEndTime": 74386
    },
    {
        "text": "...and half are able to ask for directions to a swimming pool.",
        "startTime": 49615,
        "endTime": 51827,
        "slowStartTime": 74573,
        "slowEndTime": 77965
    },
    {
        "text": "There's Hinglish, which is Hindi English,...",
        "startTime": 52357,
        "endTime": 54326,
        "slowStartTime": 78686,
        "slowEndTime": 81714
    },
    {
        "text": "...Chinglish, which is Chinese English and Singlish, which is Singaporean English,...",
        "startTime": 54582,
        "endTime": 58780,
        "slowStartTime": 82023,
        "slowEndTime": 88395
    },
    {
        "text": "...and not that bit where they speak in musicals.",
        "startTime": 58919,
        "endTime": 60964,
        "slowStartTime": 88529,
        "slowEndTime": 91671
    },
    {
        "text": "So, in conclusion, the language has got so little to do with England these days.",
        "startTime": 61463,
        "endTime": 64618,
        "slowStartTime": 92344,
        "slowEndTime": 97152
    },
    {
        "text": "It may well be time to stop calling it English.",
        "startTime": 64792,
        "endTime": 66768,
        "slowStartTime": 97338,
        "slowEndTime": 100377
    },
    {
        "text": "If someone does think up a new name for it,...",
        "startTime": 67046,
        "endTime": 68804,
        "slowStartTime": 100719,
        "slowEndTime": 103431
    },
    {
        "text": "...it should probably be in Chinese.",
        "startTime": 68975,
        "endTime": 70747,
        "slowStartTime": 103613,
        "slowEndTime": 106345
    }
]